{"tid":606511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭家純火辣回饋粉絲豪露白色內褲曝「神祕三角地帶」","createTime":"2018-03-26T13:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T14:13:10.000Z","uid":147522,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9584fa761fb60f927cabd49cac6c5ecb48329f","tid":606511,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/215938_cad51805574740a8d1b56dcf6477bc7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F215938_cad51805574740a8d1b56dcf6477bc7e.png&h=e50595c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞排妹（鄭家純）靠著火辣魔鬼E身材、天使臉孔走紅，如今正在日本遊學的她，也時常在網路上與粉絲分享近況。今（26）日雞排妹的IG破了20萬粉絲人數，為答謝粉絲的照顧，雞排妹穿著水手服，露出白色內褲，誠意十足。<br />\n雞排妹時常PO出生活照，作風親民，擁有一票死忠粉絲。如今為感謝IG人數破20萬，雞排妹不僅綁起俏麗馬尾、穿著誘人水手服，還更加碼跳躍，露出白色內褲，好身材一覽無遺。雞排妹打趣說著：「20萬人達成，謝謝大家。就用20歲時的生日祝賀圖，來應付『群賢畢至』之恩。」"},{"pid":"0aeb42fd7817305c055e3baa902a471819304313","tid":606511,"uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"條底褲仲大過某d女既熱褲"},{"pid":"a4b22871e50ce4d05fb10a6a99ac50b73752c57c","tid":606511,"uid":6497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"睇錯純官<br />\n我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae96dbfe93b513c6b0f45a6d5273fe5133cd2911","tid":606511,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"唔係我想要既家純"},{"pid":"46536099a399ac35dbc346b63ebf9b88fea0b48d","tid":606511,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:08:55.000Z","msg":"入嚟想睇新世界主席<br />\n負皮"},{"pid":"e17002f84209d79b9eb6284be184d9a782e8c483","tid":606511,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"好大個屁股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}